{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.getSparseCasesOnInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">getSparseCasesOnInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">sparseCasesOnName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.SparseCasesOnInfo\">SparseCasesOnInfo</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.getSparseCasesOnInfo","kind":"def","line":151,"name":"Lean.Meta.getSparseCasesOnInfo","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.lean#L151-L153"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.getSparseCasesOnInfoCore\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">getSparseCasesOnInfoCore</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">env</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.Environment\">Environment</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">sparseCasesOnName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.SparseCasesOnInfo\">SparseCasesOnInfo</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.getSparseCasesOnInfoCore","kind":"def","line":148,"name":"Lean.Meta.getSparseCasesOnInfoCore","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.lean#L148-L149"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.mkSparseCasesOn\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkSparseCasesOn</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">indName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ctors</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"This module creates sparse variants of `casesOn` that have arms only for some of the constructors,\noffering a catch-all.\n\nThe minor arguments come in the order of the given `ctors` array.\n\nThe catch-all provides a `Nat.hasNotBit mask x.ctorIdx` hypothesis to express that these constructors\nwere not matched. Using a single hypothesis like this, rather than many hypotheses of the form\n`x.ctorIdx ≠ i`, is important to avoid quadratic overhead in code like match splitter generation.\n\nThis function is implemented with a simple call to `.rec`, i.e. no clever branching on the constructor\nindex. The compiler has native support for these sparse matches anyways, and kernel reduction would\nnot benefit from a more sophisticated implementation unless it has itself native support for\n`.ctorIdx` and constructor elimination functions.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.mkSparseCasesOn","kind":"def","line":44,"name":"Lean.Meta.mkSparseCasesOn","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.lean#L44-L146"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.instInhabitedSparseCasesOnInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedSparseCasesOnInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.SparseCasesOnInfo\">SparseCasesOnInfo</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.instInhabitedSparseCasesOnInfo","kind":"instance","line":35,"name":"Lean.Meta.instInhabitedSparseCasesOnInfo","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.lean#L35-L35"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/SparseCasesOn.html#Lean.Meta.SparseCasesOnInfo.insterestingCtors\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">SparseCasesOnInfo</span>.<span class=\"name\">insterestingCtors</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Constructions/